  &lt;Comment&gt;
    &lt;CommentText&gt;Thank you for taking the time to post your comments regarding your Mum's recent experience whilst an inpatient at Pontefract Hospital.  I am sorry to hear of your mum's experience.

It is disappointing to read about the quality of food that you mum received on the ward and I will pass your comments onto the Catering Manager.

In terms of the TV's not working, I can only imagine how frustrating that must of been especially if there was nothing else for your mum to do all day.  I will forward your comments onto the Ward Manager so that they are aware of your mum's experience.

If you would like our Patient Liaison Team to look further into your concerns, please do not hesitate to contact them via email on myh-tr.palsmidyorks@nhs.net.

Thank you again and I wish your mum a speedy recovery.

Kind regards
Clare Blackburn
(Patient Liaison Improvement Lead)&lt;/CommentText&gt;
